# Applications Requirements:
* application should use RestApi
* Application login should be secure


# Consultancy Employe Requirements:
* should able to update the current colleges information( add, delete, update)
* should able to see the student application status
* should able to build report for a student. ( applied colleges, charges due/paid, documents needed)
* should able to build report for the consultancy operations( student accepted/rejected, commisions generated)



# Student Requirements:
* should able to see services from Consultancy
* should able to see best colleges based on Country, tuition fee, ranking, scholarships, course type
* should able to apply one or more colleges 
* should able to see the status of applied application. 
* should able to pay securely (advanced)
